imdb.title: Paradise Kiss
imdb.plot: Top high-school student seeks some purpose in life. A group of fashion design students ask her to be the front model for their clothing label "Paradise Kiss". Although she finds them weird, she accepts and soon blossoms as a person.

episodes.title: Atelier
episodes.plot: Yukari is a high school student preparing for a college entrance exam. One day she is approached by a group of fashion design students, who ask her to become their model.

episodes.title: Illumination
episodes.plot: Yukari is trying to focus on studying, but she can't stop thinking about her meeting with the Paradise Kiss designers. While talking to George she realizes that she doesn't really know what she wants to do with her life.

episodes.title: KISS
episodes.plot: Yukari and Miwako meet for tea. Yukari comes to the meeting with Hiroyuki, her classmate and Miwako's childhood friend.

episodes.title: George
episodes.plot: The designers are working on a fabric they want to use for their show. Yukari is uncertain about her own feelings for George.

episodes.title: Mother
episodes.plot: Yukari tells her mother the truth about her involvement with Paradise Kiss. After an argument, she decides to leave home and quit school to focus on becoming a model.

episodes.title: New World
episodes.plot: Pursuing her career as a model, Yukari goes to her first photo session. She and George grow closer to each other.

episodes.title: Butterfly
episodes.plot: Yukari moves in with George. Miwako's sister tells her about an agency looking for new models.

episodes.title: Tokumori
episodes.plot: Yukari is informed that being underage she can't join a modeling agency without her parents' permission. Hiroyuki is worried about Yukari and wants to meet with her.

episodes.title: Designer
episodes.plot: Yukari's mother agrees to meet with a president of a model agency if Yukari graduates from high school. The designers face an unforeseen obstacle in completing an outfit for their show.

episodes.title: Rose
episodes.plot: It's the day of the show and the designers are painting white roses blue to fit George's vision. Yukari is anxious about walking the runway for the first time in her life. Isabella tells Yukari about her childhood.

episodes.title: Stage
episodes.plot: Yukari walks the runway in George's dress. After the show she feels conflicted about its results.George meets his friend, who came from London to see the show.

episodes.title: Future
episodes.plot: Yukari and the designers celebrate Christmas. George is considering different options for his career after graduation.
